Name: tick-hunter
About the game: Tik-hunter - first-person game with elements of horror. You are the only survivor on this island, when you have nothing left you decided to get out of the sewers and try to get out of this cemetery. There are lots of weapons, enemies and so on. The difficulty makes you need to find a way out of the gate. Can you get out?
